{"lemma":"جَرْيُ","slug":"جَرْيُ","root":"ج.ر.#","root_slug":"ج-ر-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ر-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جَرْيُ","root":"جري","pos":"V","occurrence_count":57},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n5394","n5639","n5622","n5623","n5630","n5634"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D9%8A%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَرَى (jarā) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"course, run"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"watercourse"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"diarrhea, dysentery"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"alternative form of جِرِّيث (jirrīṯ, “slime eel”)","tags":["alt-of","alternative"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n5394","headword_ar":"جِرِّىٌّ","root":"jr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(written in the Towsheeh with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"j","text_ar":"ج"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, TA,) [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eel;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a kind of fish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long and smooth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling the serpent, and called in Persian"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAro maAhiY","text_ar":"مَارْ مَاهِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; said to be a dial. var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jir~iyvN","text_ar":"جِرِّيثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not eaten by the Jews,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and forbidden to be eaten by 'Alee;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having no scales:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any fish having no scales."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Towsheeh, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n5639","headword_ar":"جِرِّىٌّ","root":"jrY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eel;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain fish, well known."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K: mentioned also in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jr","text_ar":"جر"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n5622","headword_ar":"جَرَى","root":"jrY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", said of water (S, Mgh, Msb) &c., (S,) or of water and the like, (K,) more properly thus, as in the K, aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaroYN","text_ar":"جَرْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarayaAnN","text_ar":"جَرَيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiroyapN","text_ar":"جِرْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, * Msb, K,) [which last see below,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It ran,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passed along quickly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"originally said of water: (Er-Rághib, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it flowed;;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAla","text_ar":"سَالَ"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqafa","text_ar":"وَقَفَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sakana","text_ar":"سَكَنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) ―         -b2-  Said also of farina, in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraY Ald~aqiyqu fiY Als~unobuli","text_ar":"جَرَى الدَّقِيقُ فِى السُّنْبُلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The farina pervaded the ears of wheat"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qmH","text_ar":"قمح"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  And of a horse (Mgh, Msb, K) and the like, (Msb, K,) aor. as above, (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaroYN","text_ar":"جَرْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarayaAnN","text_ar":"جَرَيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiraA='N","text_ar":"جِرَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majorFY","text_ar":"مَجْرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ran;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] from the same verb said of water. (Mgh) ―         -b4-  And of a ship: you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarati Als~afiynapN","text_ar":"جَرَتِ السَّفِينَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaroYN","text_ar":"جَرْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majorFY","text_ar":"مَجْرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ship ran."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b5-  And of the sun, and a star: you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarati Al$~amosu","text_ar":"جَرَتِ الشَّمْسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaroYN","text_ar":"جَرْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sun pursued its course:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarati Aln~ujuwmu","text_ar":"جَرَتِ النُّجُومُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The stars travelled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passed along, from east to west."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraY A_ilaY ka*aA","text_ar":"جَرَى اـِلَى كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, and Har p. 152,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaroYN","text_ar":"جَرْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiraA='N","text_ar":"جِرَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjrY","text_ar":"اجرى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ijoraA='N","text_ar":"اـِجْرَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Ham p. 224, and Har p. 152;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He betook,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"directed, himself to such a thing; made it his object; aimed at it; intended,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"purposed, it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, and Har ubi suprà:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he hastened to it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) but in the latter phrase, an objective complement is understood; and it is used in relation to something disapproved, or disliked; (Ham and Har;) properly,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjrY fiEolahu A_ilayoh","text_ar":"اجرى فِعْلَهُ اـِلَيْه"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ham,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjrY fiEolahu biAlqaSodi A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اجرى فِعْلَهُ بِالقَصْدِ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Har.) ―         -b7-  Hence, perhaps, the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraY AlxilaAfu fiY ka*aA","text_ar":"جَرَى الخِلَافُ فِى كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  [frequently used as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A controversy ran,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ran on, respecting such a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"between such and such persons]. (Msb.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraY lahu Al$~aYo'u","text_ar":"جَرَى لَهُ الشَّىْءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sh, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraY Ealayohi","text_ar":"جَرَى عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The thing was permanent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"continued, to him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, TA.) [And, more commonly, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The thing happened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occurred, to him."},{"kind":"text","text":"Whence, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAjarayaAtN","text_ar":"مَاجَرَيَاتٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAjaraY","text_ar":"مَاجَرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", used as a single word, by late writers, meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Events,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occurrences."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yajoriY","text_ar":"هُوَ يَجْرِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majoraAhu","text_ar":"مَجْرَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It is like it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"similar to it, in state, condition, case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"predicament."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a word or phrase)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"follows the same rule"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rules,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occupies the same grammatical place, as it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(another word or phrase). And similar to this is the saying,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mujaAraApa AlmabiyEi","text_ar":"مُجَارَاةَ المَبِيعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~ayonu waAlr~ahonu yatajaArayaAni","text_ar":"الدَّيْنُ وَالرَّهْنُ يَتَجَارَيَانِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wAlv~amani","text_ar":"والثَّمَنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The debt and the pledge are subject to the same laws as the thing sold and the price"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.) ―         -b10-  [Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It acts as,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a similar manner to, it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he acts in his stead:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jariY~N","text_ar":"جَرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". Hence the phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraY minohu majoraY ka*aA","text_ar":"جَرَى مِنْهُ مَجْرَى كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It acted upon him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affected him, like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a similar manner to, such a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the prov.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraY minohu majoraY All~aduwdi","text_ar":"جَرَى مِنْهُ مَجْرَى اللَّدُودِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It acted upon him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affected him, like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"similarly to, the medicine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"draught, called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ldwd","text_ar":"لدود"},{"kind":"text","text":":"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mnh","text_ar":"منه"},{"kind":"text","text":"here having the meaning of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi","text_ar":"فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (ISk, S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ld","text_ar":"لد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b11-  [One says, also, of an inf. n., and of a part. n., that is regularly formed,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yajoriY EalaY AlfiEoli","text_ar":"يَجْرِى عَلَى الفِعْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It is conformable to the verb."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","TA","Lth","Ham","Sh"]},{"entry_id":"n5623","headword_ar":"جرّى","root":"jrY","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sent a deputy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"commissioned agent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjirY","text_ar":"اجِرى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jr~Y jariy~FA","text_ar":"جرّى جَرِيًّا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appointed, a deputy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"commissioned agent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S, * TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstjrAhu","text_ar":"استجراهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, * TA.) Hence the trad., (TA,) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yasotajoriyan~akumu","text_ar":"لَا يَسْتَجْرِيَنَّكُمُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~ayoTiAnu","text_ar":"الشَّيْطِانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"By no means let the Devil make you his followers and his commissioned agents."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY HaAjatihi","text_ar":"فِى حَاجَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjrAhu","text_ar":"اجراهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sent him to accomplish his needful affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S"]},{"entry_id":"n5630","headword_ar":"جَرًى","root":"jrY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraA^'N","text_ar":"جَرَاءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"-A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalotuhu mino jaraAka","text_ar":"فَعَلْتُهُ مِنْ جَرَاكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn","text_ar":"من"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraAy^ika","text_ar":"جَرَايِكَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I did it because of thee,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of thine act; on thine account;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for thy sake; i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn","text_ar":"من"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajolika","text_ar":"اَجْلِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn jar~aAka","text_ar":"من جَرَّاكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which see in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jr","text_ar":"جر"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n5634","headword_ar":"جَرِىٌّ","root":"jrY","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A commissioned agent; a factor; a deputy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K:) because he runs in the affairs of him who appoints him, (Mgh,) or acts in his stead ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yajoriY majoraAhu","text_ar":"يَجْرِى مَجْرَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (S, Mgh:) [in this and other senses following] used alike as sing. and pl., and also as [masc. and] fem.: (K:) but sometimes, though rarely,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jariy~apN","text_ar":"جَرِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used for the fem., accord. to AHát; and accord. to J [in the S, and Mtr in the Mgh], it has"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajoriyaA='u","text_ar":"اَجْرِيَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"for its pl. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A messenger,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"person sent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that runs in an affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) But accord. to Er-Rághib, it is weaker [in signification, or in point of chasteness,] than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasuwlN","text_ar":"رَسُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wakiylN","text_ar":"وَكِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which are given as its syns. in the S and K]. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A servant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hired man; a hireling."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kr, K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A surety; a guarantee; one who is responsible, accountable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"answerable, for another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, K.)       -A2-  The word signifying “ bold, ” or “ daring, ” is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jariYo'N","text_ar":"جَرِىْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","K"]}]}}